---
import Divider from "../../common/Divider.astro";
---

<Divider caseStudies={true} />
<section class="container py-[40px] md:py-[64px]">
  <div class="grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <h2
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] font-light uppercase triangle-text-after text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      The Starting Point
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[24px] md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="font-neue-montreal font-medium text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[1.2] text-white">
        What I inherited
      </h3>
      <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[18px] md:text-[22px] leading-[1.5] text-white/80">
        The brand had a genuinely premium physical product — handcrafted teak cold
        plunges built in Bali — and almost no digital presence to match. The
        existing Shopify store was half-finished, visually broken, and crucially
        wasn't indexed by Google. There was no funnel, no lead capture, and no
        acquisition strategy. From a growth standpoint, the brand was starting at
        zero.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
